dit rate派息，通常有最低保證rate. 你有flexibility 去再入錢top up，調整投資同保險成分，所以叫萬用壽險.<br />\n<br />\n儲蓄保如果係長期嘅，最常見係擺錢入去，會有個保證價值，同埋有個非保證dividend. 個dividend會因應保險公司投資同賠錢經驗去調整。早走都幾乎肯定蝕錢。分分鐘廿年先保證回本。而且張單應該入唔到錢top up, 但可以買多張。<br />\n<br />\n至於係咪trap, 你應該睇真啲條款。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n通常死先賠錢，所以應該無本人claim到答到你問題。不過有啲絕症或者全身殘廢都可以提前claim足。死嘅話應該都叫有賺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n你留意下singapore同bermuda啲產品，有需要可以聯絡broker<br />\n或者你上網睇入場費<br />\n<br />\n通常吸引嘅門檻都高"},{"pid":"b43f25efa28f40e0521d7435d41570b0d6378925","tid":2086705,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"係另一個post一轉貼完實單出黎就好多保險狗出黎護航, 呢下呢個post又有冇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote>呢個blog貼左簽名張單同埋今日非保證變成幾多 好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算死撚咗都小左30幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩個仔冇得讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hksufm.blogspot.com/2020/06/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksufm.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F06%2Fblog-post.html&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F4yfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=1eb09474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hksufm.blogspot.com/2020/06/blog-post.html</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-u4pPgmgHCEM/Xu9kdw2QGTI/AAAAAAAACBY/syuzdqA14GQmZfQCsVu1yPFVhSudW_wYQCK4BGAsYHg/s2880/螢幕截圖+2020-06-21+下午9.41.40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-u4pPgmgHCEM%2FXu9kdw2QGTI%2FAAAAAAAACBY%2FsyuzdqA14GQmZfQCsVu1yPFVhSudW_wYQCK4BGAsYHg%2Fs2880%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%2B2020-06-21%2B%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%889.41.40.png&h=2960e4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JWdk7f47Pbg/Xqa5BF5sCfI/AAAAAAAAB-w/PC-lxWqSfC8ToR4alHUsSSjzXcp8Z6Q9gCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/螢幕截圖+2020-04-27+下午6.50.26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna